'''Kadok Resources''' was a [[Bitthævrian/Legends|Bitthævrian]]-controlled company.

After some unfortunate experiences with Imperial-backed mining companies wanting to operate in [[Guiteica/Legends|Guiteica]] (particularly [[Vulca Minerals]] adopting a pushy attitude about [[yttrium]] mining), Kadok Resources was assigned to manage all of Guiteica's exports.

